
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Information
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Biblestudy-Tool is used to do quick look-ups and note taking with references to 
the scriptures.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This requires a JRE installed somewhere on your system and the java executable 
be available on the PATH.  The backing database used by the product is an 
embedded derby database and it will be setup and managed by the product.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Open the projects in Eclipse.
2. Set your target platform to the one provided.
3. Do an export to whatever platform you need.
